reviewText: Actually, I love the movie, but the description of this particular item is highly misg. It is advertised as Multi-Languag, but the only language is French (unless you count the "FBI Warning" in English. There is no dubbed English and no subtitles. The descriptuion ought to clearly say that it is French only..

This review is for the Collection Axia Films release of Jour de Fete.  The print is in beautiful condition but there are no subtitles available.  If you speak French, no problem, but again, no English subtitles are provided.  Not much plot to this movie so not a huge deal, still subtitles would have been nice.
